    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices in which the candle is enclosed in a metal tube with a wick hole at the top and a coiled spring at the base of the candle to push it up as it burns.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
